reviewText: So good to hear Reagan's voice, and what a real presesident sounds like.
This is something I go back to many, many times.  To me it is just sound philosophy regardless . . .
This is a wonderful set!  It does not get any better than this!  I really enjoyed watching the dvds.  They were of very good quality and it brought back memories of those wonderful times.  Thank you.
In this volatile political climate it was great to be inspired by these inspirational speeches.  If only we had this kind of patriotism and courage today!
